additionalInfo.description:
This is the user defined function for checking the list of value DQM on column with string type.

Input : 

Attribute : Attribute on which LOV check is to be applied.

IsMandatory: FALSE if this attribute is optional in the implementation. TRUE if this attribute is mandatory. If FALSE then null value will be considered as valid value.

Value1 to Value8 : List of valid values for this attribute. if implementation does not have all 8 values in the valid list then user can place two single quotes (blank) in place of these values.

Return type : Numeric indicating 0 (FALSE) as invalid and 1 (TRUE) as valid.
